    <item>
      <title>加拿大遭竞争对手乳制品出口商指控倾销乳制品</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/canada-accused-by-rival-dairy-exporters-of-dumping-milk-products</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰、澳大利亚和美国乳制品公司指责加拿大向国际市场倾销低价乳制品，并要求其政府进行干预。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/canada-accused-by-rival-dairy-exporters-of-dumping-milk-products</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 21:26:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢比奥暗示特朗普可能将古巴重新列入恐怖主义名单</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/rubio-signals-trump-is-likely-to-return-cuba-to-terrorism-list</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普提名他担任美国最高外交官，这表明这位当选总统很可能会在下周就职后推翻乔·拜登总统周二做出的将古巴从支持恐怖主义国家名单中删除的决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/rubio-signals-trump-is-likely-to-return-cuba-to-terrorism-list</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 21:06:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普与丹麦领导人通话讨论格陵兰岛问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/trump-discussed-greenland-interest-in-call-with-danish-leader</link>
      <description><![CDATA[丹麦首相梅特·弗雷德里克森周三与美国新任总统进行了 45 分钟的电话交谈后表示，唐纳德·特朗普证实他有意为美国收购格陵兰岛。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/trump-discussed-greenland-interest-in-call-with-danish-leader</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 20:52:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列与哈马斯达成停火协议暂停加沙战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/israel-hamas-agree-gaza-ceasefire-deal-in-wind-down-of-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列和哈马斯达成停火协议，要求释放数十名人质并暂时停止加沙地带的战争。这场战争在过去 15 个月内已造成数万人死亡，并引发了整个中东地区更广泛的动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/israel-hamas-agree-gaza-ceasefire-deal-in-wind-down-of-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 17:00:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普回归之际，韩国总统被捕事件暴露危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/president-s-arrest-shows-south-korea-in-peril-as-trump-returns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国调查人员周三成功逮捕了被弹劾的总统尹锡烈，同时避免了首尔市中心发生暴力冲突。但该国的麻烦还远未结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/president-s-arrest-shows-south-korea-in-peril-as-trump-returns</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
